**ttak_tam_tam**
- [ vīṭṭutteyvam ]
பெ. id.+.
1. household deity; குடும்பதேவதை. loc
2. woman who dies during the lifetime ofher husband and is worshipped as a deityby her family. பார். மங்கலியப்பெண்டு. tj

**சென்னைப் பல்கலைக்கழகத் தமிழ்ப் பேரகராதி**
- - vīṭṭu-t-teyvam
- n. <</>id.+
- 1. Household-deity;
- குடும்பதேவதை. Loc.
- 2. Woman who dies during the lifetime of her husband and is worshipped as a deity by her family.
- See மங்கலியப்பெண்டு. Tj.

